Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:49.45,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}You held out a small hand
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.58,0:20:51.34,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}Smiling wide to you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.41,0:20:55.34,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}It was so natural
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.92,0:21:00.51,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}It may have no meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.74,0:21:06.28,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}But it is something I cannot do
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.61,0:21:12.35,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}You touched my hand without thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.35,0:21:16.14,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}That it was nice for me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.07,0:21:24.46,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}All the times we believed
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.58,0:21:32.71,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}That the words in our hands we will draw
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.84,0:21:40.91,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}Maybe it wasn't 'cause\N you're holding my hand now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.10,0:21:52.03,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}Every moment, everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.17,0:21:57.40,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}I can feel, I can feel
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.73,0:22:02.58,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}When I'm holding you from bad
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.64,0:22:09.95,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}You will learn
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:49.45,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}你伸出的稚嫩雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.58,0:20:51.34,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}一如那燦爛的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.41,0:20:55.34,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}那樣自然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.92,0:21:00.51,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}也許沒有過多的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.74,0:21:06.28,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}卻讓我可望而不可即
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.61,0:21:12.35,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}你輕觸我的掌心 不帶一絲猶疑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.35,0:21:16.14,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}撫慰著我的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.07,0:21:24.46,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}我們始終堅信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.58,0:21:32.71,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}手心的誓言 是未來的藍圖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.84,0:21:40.91,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}但此刻 我只想擁有你的溫熱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.10,0:21:52.03,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}無論何時 無論何地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.17,0:21:57.40,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}我都可以感知到你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.73,0:22:02.58,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}當我從逆境中將你扶起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.64,0:22:09.95,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}你將懂得我的心意
